				<h1>DB HealthWatch</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">GenAI-Powered Database Diagnostics Platform</p>

				<h2>The Problem</h2>
				<p>
					Database administrators and DevOps teams spend hours manually analyzing AWR reports, 
					performance logs, and system metrics to diagnose issues. The process is tedious, 
					error-prone, and requires deep domain expertise. Critical performance degradations 
					often go unnoticed until they impact production systems.
				</p>

				<h2>The Solution</h2>
				<p>
					DB HealthWatch is an intelligent GenAI assistant that transforms database diagnostics 
					through natural language interaction and automated analysis. Built with LangChain, 
					GPT-4, and FAISS, the platform enables engineers to query complex database metrics 
					using plain English and receive actionable insights in seconds.
				</p>

				<h2>Key Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Natural Language Querying</strong>: Ask questions like "What caused the CPU spike at 3 AM?" and get context-aware answers</li>
					<li><strong>Proactive Alerting</strong>: Automated classification system (Good, Warning, Critical) with intelligent threshold detection</li>
					<li><strong>Specialized Agents</strong>: Dedicated analysis modules for CPU load, memory usage, I/O patterns, and query performance</li>
					<li><strong>Automated Email Reports</strong>: Rich context alerts with recommendations sent to relevant teams</li>
					<li><strong>RAG Architecture</strong>: Retrieval Augmented Generation for accurate, hallucination-free diagnostics</li>
				</ul>

